page.title: 10Barby Junior Soccer Club
page.content: {Under 10's} The Under 10's train on a Saturday from 10.30-11.30a.m. The under 10's have got about 15 members. There are 2 people in control: Mr.Rose and Mr.Mills. {Under 11's} The under 11's train at the same time as the under 10's. It is run by Mr.McGuire and Mr.McMahon. The fees are 20p for training and 30p for a match. It costs Â£1.50 to sign on. We play in the Daventry League. The players all come from Kilsby or Barby except one who comes from Braunston. Most boys come from Kilsby. Nearly all the Barby team play for Kilsby School. {Next Year Next year we will play in the Rugby League. The club's under 13 team has had to stop because of lack of support. We are quite a good team.
